    "description": {
        "en-US": "WideGPT adds a slider for adjusting the width of ChatGPT answer space to the top of the ChatGPT window. Now works with both the free and paid versions of ChatGPT.\n\nSource is available on <a href=\"https://prod.outgoing.prod.webservices.mozgcp.net/v1/d10f677cfcec2f4d2f220bdb8b7ffd5e92e7a76210ae5230477120455037baa7/https%3A//github.com/fuzzcan/WideGPT\" rel=\"nofollow\">GitHub</a>."
    },
    "developer_comments": {
        "en-US": "IMPORTANT NOTICE FOR EXISTING USERS: OpenAI changed ChatGPT's url, which breaks the domain-specific permissions granted to WideGPT by Firefox. Because of this, you will need to give permission to WideGPT to access data on the new domain. In Firefox, go to add-ons and themes &gt; WideGPT &gt; Manage, click the gear icon, and select \"Check for updates...\". You will be prompted to grant permission for WideGPT to access data on the new url."
    },
